{"version":1,"source":"indexeddb-geo2025-snapshot","modified":1782096381181,"work":{"id":361988,"cn":"章鱼噼的原罪","en":"Takopi's Original Sin","title":"タコピーの原罪","city":"北海道","color":"#d13f88","cover":"/images/bangumi/361988.jpg","fade":6.7,"cat":"漫画系列","geo":[41.882856,140.739336],"zoom":9.5,"points":[{"id":"o6ce7h1sx","geo":[41.878062,140.706866],"priority":3281,"name":"あかまつ公園","isFolder":false,"uid":1751,"image":"/images/user/1751/bangumi/361988/points/o6ce7h1sx-1726347116121.jpg","ep":1,"s":"","mark":"章鱼噼的土管位于町立南公园，追赶他的是町立保健所（保健所属于振兴局管辖，所以町立保健所是虚构的），因此函馆市和北斗市可以排除。\n\n七饭町、森町、鹿部、厚沢部附近是候选地，但如果东直树の地图比较准确的话，那么就是七饭町或森町其中一个。\n\n如果南公园位于城镇的南侧，那么从城镇的开阔程度来看，七饭町的可能性更高。土管是藤子不二雄的致敬作品，所以如果认为它并不存在的话，那么赤松公园就非常符合了。\n\n那里有栅栏、柱状钟表，以及从高处俯瞰的道路，树木零星地生长着。虽然没有书中描绘得那么茂密，但还是比较接近的。","origin":"Yas_Yam@Yas_Yam3","originLink":"https://x.com/Yas_Yam3/status/1501183916236886017?t=EyfNXt4rKHkqlGJ780r0Dw&s=19","density":692812,"originURL":"https://x.com/Yas_Yam3/status/1501183916236886017?t=EyfNXt4rKHkqlGJ780r0Dw&s=19"},{"id":"o6culn8p7","geo":[35.700394,139.816158],"priority":79,"name":"Brillia​タワー​東京","isFolder":false,"uid":1751,"image":"/images/user/1751/bangumi/361988/points/o6culn8p7-1726348131095.jpg","ep":11,"s":"","origin":"そらみ（曽良 峰子）@quickgirl17","originLink":"https://x.com/quickgirl17/status/1494802083026927619?t=jOG4U0kxGJMRaFumzn_M5g&s=19","density":13730,"originURL":"https://x.com/quickgirl17/status/1494802083026927619?t=jOG4U0kxGJMRaFumzn_M5g&s=19"},{"id":"o6czzbbd0","geo":[35.659475,139.69943],"priority":4,"name":"SHIBUYA109前","isFolder":false,"uid":1751,"image":"/images/user/1751/bangumi/361988/points/o6czzbbd0-1726348389594.jpg","ep":10,"s":"","density":13730,"origin":"@孤光明谷","originURL":""}],"tags":[],"priority":11740,"icon":null,"tAbbr":"タコピー","theme":{"src":"/images/ptheme/361988_100_76.webp?v=heenv","ids":["o6ce7h1sx","o6culn8p7","o6czzbbd0"],"modified":1753539595788,"w":100,"h":76},"modified":1781696246181,"pointsLength":3,"imagesLength":3},"points":[{"id":"o6ce7h1sx","geo":[41.8